General Content:
Science and our mental projections are not

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:57.109
connected to higher, living force, so they
fail us.

00:00:57.109 --> 00:01:02.929
Biological movement within us is spiral, but
mental projections are linear, dead.

00:01:02.929 --> 00:01:09.929
We must become scientists of the Divine, and
understand the knowledge of the roots.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:17.120
We are all One; all of God’s children – no
nationalities exist.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:24.120
You can find information about the Holy Ghost
in the Bible, but you must go to Indian scriptures

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:32.640
to find information about the ‘Adi Shakti’.
Doctors must learn about the three sides of

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:39.320
a human: physical, mental and emotional.
With Sahaja Yoga you can cure yourself and

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:42.890
others.
You cannot pay for Kundalini rising – if

00:01:42.890 --> 00:01:48.000
you could, or did, it would no longer be benevolent.

